title: HUMAN EVENTS DAILY: NOV 2 2021 - KYLE RITTENHOUSE TRIAL: NEVER-BEFORE-SEEN FBI FOOTAGE OF SHOOTING
description:
On today’s episode of Human Events Daily, Jack gives you the latest developments in the Kyle Rittenhouse Trial, along with NEVER-BEFORE-SEEN footage of shooting, 18 NYC fire stations shut down after firefighters are sent home after refusing the vaccine,  U.S trained Afghan special forces are joining ISIS for protection against the Taliban, and convicted murderer Rodney Reed is denied retrial. 



Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
